Class LabeledGraphIntString

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class LabeledGraphIntString
extends org.apache.flink.api.java.tuple.Tuple2<int[],String[]>
    Minimalistic model of a graph with integer-labeled vertices and string-labeld edges. f0: [sourceId_k,sourceLabel_k,targetId_k,targetLabel_k,..] f1: [edgeLabel_0,..,edgeLabel_k]
